  "text": "Apple's revenue performance in Q3 2025 showed modest contraction, with total revenue of $94,036,000,000 representing a -1.39% year-over-year decline according to the YoY growth calculation. This compares to Q2 2025 revenue of $95,359,000,000, indicating sequential pressure as well. The revenue trend suggests the company is facing headwinds in top-line growth, potentially reflecting mature product cycles or competitive pressures in key markets.",
